// All effects written in Quanta shader language, compiled to HLSL/GLSL.
//
// CATEGORIES:
// - Color Processing (20 effects)
// - Tonemapping (13 effects)
// - Lighting & Shadows (15 effects)
// - Post-Processing (25 effects)
// - Film & Cinematic (15 effects)
// - Utility & Debug (20 effects)
